<section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 text-[var(--secondary)]">
  <header class="mb-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-secondary">API - Brainrots (Uso de GET)</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-[var(--thirty)]">
      Esta API expone recursos de "brainrot" usando únicamente el método GET.
    </p>
  </header>

  <!-- Descripción general -->
  <div class="bg-[var(--fourty)]/30 backdrop-blur-md border border-[var(--fourty)] rounded-2xl p-6 mb-8 shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_6px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)]">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary">Descripción general</h2>
    <p class="text-[var(--thirty)] mt-2">Los usuarios pueden:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[var(--secondary)] mt-3 space-y-1">
      <li>Obtener <span class="font-medium">toda la información</span> de la lista completa.</li>
      <li>Filtrar <span class="font-medium">objetos específicos</span> usando <em>parámetros de consulta</em>.</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="backdrop-blur-md bg-gradient-to-bl from-[var(--thirty)]/40 to-[var(--thirty)]/20 px-2 py-4 my-3 rounded-md overflow-x-auto text-[var(--secondary)]">
      Nota: Algunos campos como <code>lyrics</code>, <code>history</code> o <code>personality</code> contienen texto extenso.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Endpoint base -->
  <div class="bg-[var(--fourty)]/30 backdrop-blur-md border border-[var(--fourty)] rounded-2xl p-6 mb-8 shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_6px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)]">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary">Endpoint base</h2>
    <Prism lang='http' code=`GET https://the-brainrots-almanac/api/brainrots` class='backdrop-blur-md bg-gradient-to-bl from-[var(--thirty)]/40 to-[var(--thirty)]/20 px-2 py-4 my-3 rounded-md overflow-x-auto text-[var(--secondary)]'/>
  </div>

  <!-- Parámetros de consulta -->
  <div class="bg-[var(--fourty)]/30 backdrop-blur-md border border-[var(--fourty)] rounded-2xl p-6 mb-8 shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_6px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)]">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary">Uso de GET con parámetros de consulta</h2>
    <p class="text-[var(--thirty)] mt-2">Puedes filtrar resultados con parámetros en la URL:</p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-6">
      <div class="p-4 backdrop-blur-md bg-gradient-to-bl from-[var(--thirty)]/40 to-[var(--thirty)]/20 px-2 py-4 my-3 rounded-md overflow-x-auto text-[var(--secondary)] bg-transparent">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-fourty">name</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--thirty)] mt-1">Se refiere al <strong>slug</strong> del objeto.</p>
        <Prism lang='http' code='GET /api/brainrots?name=bambini-crostini' class='mt-6 overflow-x-autotext-[var(--secondary)]'/>
      </div>

      <div class="p-4 backdrop-blur-md bg-gradient-to-bl from-[var(--thirty)]/40 to-[var(--thirty)]/20 px-2 py-4 my-3 rounded-md overflow-x-auto text-[var(--secondary)]">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-fourty">key</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--thirty)] mt-1">Se refiere a la propiedad <code>data.key</code>.</p>
        <Prism lang='http' code='GET /api/brainrots?key=20' class='mt-6 text-[var(--secondary)]'/>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-fourty">Combinando filtros</h3>
      <Prism lang='http' code='GET /api/brainrots?name=fluri-frulla&key=4' class='backdrop-blur-md bg-gradient-to-bl from-[var(--thirty)]/40 to-[var(--thirty)]/20 px-2 py-4 my-3 rounded-md overflow-x-auto text-[var(--secondary)]'/>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Ejemplos -->
  <div class="bg-[var(--fourty)]/30 backdrop-blur-md border border-[var(--fourty)] rounded-2xl p-6 mb-8 shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_6px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)]">
