    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Salida</h2>

    <h3 class="mt-4 font-medium text-fourty">1. Solicitud (fetch)</h3>
    <Prism lang='http' code='GET https://the-brainrots-almanac/api/brainrots?name=trulimero-trulichina' class='backdrop-blur-md bg-gradient-to-bl from-[var(--thirty)]/40 to-[var(--thirty)]/20 px-2 py-4 my-3 rounded-md overflow-x-auto text-[var(--secondary)]'/>

    <h3 class="mt-4 font-medium text-fourty">2. Respuesta</h3>
    <Prism lang='js' code={outputExample} class='backdrop-blur-md bg-gradient-to-bl from-[var(--thirty)]/40 to-[var(--thirty)]/20 px-2 py-4 my-3 rounded-md overflow-x-auto text-[var(--secondary)]'/>
  </div>

  <!-- Errores -->
  <div class="bg-[var(--fourty)]/30 backdrop-blur-md border border-[var(--fourty)] rounded-2xl p-6 mb-8 shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] hover:shadow-[0_6px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)]">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary">Errores y comportamiento</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-[var(--secondary)] mt-3 space-y-2">
      <li>Si no se encuentran resultados, devuelve <code>[]</code>.</li>
      <li>Si el <code>slug</code> no existe, devuelve <code>404 Not Found</code> con un JSON explicativo.</li>
      <li>Solo se aceptan métodos <code>GET</code>. Los demás devuelven <code>405 Method Not Allowed</code>.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>